snippet.title: Refugee The 2nd Hearing V3_2
snippet.description:
www.quitesoulless.com/refugee.htm
Hey!

Here is the 3rd episode of the 'Refugee: ..." game published, you may find at 
12min43sec-14min56sec

Dumping judge Isabel Bronzina from the court on the cross of 6th and Olive, LA is all back in this episode in the desert.

I am the mental patient (with schizophrenia), I was trying to show to the US attorneys that I am not mentally sick, but Chief LA ICE Counsel managed to find for me judge Isabel Bronzina with grant rate of 1.4%, who fast and efficiently issued the removal order of me back to the isolation mental ward in Russia.

I put the appeal to the Attorney General Assistants and I live in the US without work permit for 2 years as ICE and Homeland Security are trying to freeze me, they put up 58 pages of impeachment against me as a mental patient which may be found here www.quitesoulless.com/making.htm

Also I was under the surveilance of most likely the FBI - about this here
www.quitesoulless.com/ref2making.htm

Vasily Zotov

The game can be downloaded here
www.quitesoulless.com/refugee.htm
